{"tid":1436103,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【再咁落去就輸】應對港共洗腦文宣手法","createTime":"2019-08-09T08:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:21:44.000Z","uid":85252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd85a54b1d37acb5bf976a8e809d6eef882f786","tid":1436103,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"暫時見到港共政權洗腦文宣有四大重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴力、仇恨、經濟、穩定</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要重整用語回擊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟用嘅係最低武力</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察就係用過份暴力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟心中嘅係義憤</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭對港人就係仇恨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爭取普選留住外資</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支爆近了，港共要抽乾香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">普選先可以長治久安</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共要香港變新疆</span></span><br />\n自中聯辦研討會後，港共政權統一戰線後，可以見到港共文宣的火力已經全開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要記住﹗呢次輸咗，兄弟就會有排被清算﹗"},{"pid":"0a1c4b6282d78a14a3b3a9e1517cda7fe9f86dc1","tid":1436103,"uid":89974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接做圖啦，大家知點打而家係無人落手做"}]}